---
import iconos from "../components/icons.jsx"
const Icon1 = iconos[0].icon
const Icon2 = iconos[1].icon
const Icon3 = iconos[2].icon

import cathome from "../../public/images/catinhome.jpg"
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
---

<section class='benefits'>
  <div class='b_image'>
    <Image src={cathome} alt='cat' />
  </div>
  <div class='b_text'>
    <div>
      <h2>Benefits of having a cat at home</h2>
      <p>
        Cats are very independent animals, but they're also very affectionate
        and grateful. Having a cat at home can be a very rewarding experience.
        Here are some benefits of having a cat at home:
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
          <Icon1 />
        </p>
        Reduces stress: A cat's purr has a calming effect and can reduce anxiety.
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <Icon2 />
        </p>
        Improves health: Studies have shown that living with cats can lower blood
        pressure and the risk of heart disease.
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <Icon3 />
        </p>
        They always make you smile: Their wit and pranks are an antidote to a bad
        mood.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  section {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    color: var(--text);
    > div {
      width: 50%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    img {
      width: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(
        to right,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 1) 70%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)
      );
    }
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5em, 2.5vw, 2em);
  }

  .b_text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    padding-left: 3em;
  }
  ul {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    gap: 0.4em;
  }
  li {
    list-style: none;
    width: 33%;
    font-size: 0.7em;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    padding: 2em 0.5em;
    border-radius: 1em;
    position: relative;
    outline: 1px solid var(--gray);
    transition: outline 0.5s ease;
    &:hover {
      outline-width: 5px;
    }
    &:nth-child(1):hover {
      outline-color: rgb(235, 24, 94);
    }
    &:nth-child(2):hover {
      outline-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);
    }
    &:nth-child(3):hover {
      outline-color: rgb(231, 112, 0);
    }
    & > * {
      transition: 0.4s ease-in-out;
    }
    &:hover > * {
      transform: scale(1.4);
    }

    & p {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
